<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>frḥẗ qlby byk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- frḥẗ qlby byk ʿmry klh lyk
 frḥẗ qlby byk ʿmry klh byk yạ yswʿ wlyk
 1- (lmạ knt tạyh mskyn fy ạlʿạlm wḥzyn
 jyt ly yạrby bḥb kbyr frḥtny ktyr)2
 2- (ṣlybk kạn mkạny fdytny yạ njạty
 ḥmytny mn ạlmwt yạrby wạ̹tạ̉lmt bdạly)2</lyrics>
